<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>What Music - Rzkyy</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>What Music</h1>
    <div class="overlay">
      <div class="fixed-top text-center">
        <p>Rzkyy Dev.</p>
    </div>
      <div class="overlay__inner">
        <h1 class="overlay__title">
          Hai, kamu hanya mempunyai setengah lirik lagu?
          Gunakan <span class="text-gradient">What Music</span> agar kamu dapat menemukannya
        </h1>
        <p class="overlay__description">
          upload file disini dengan berdurasi 15-30 sebagai sample audio, pastikan audio berformat mp3</strong>
        </p>
        <form action="/result" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <div class="input-group mb-3">
          <input type="file" name="file"  accept=".mp3" id="file" class="form-control" id="inputGroupFile02" required>
        </div>
        <div class="overlay__btns">
          <button type="submit" onclick="ubah(this)" id="btn" class="overlay__btn">
            Submit
          </button>
        </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script>
     function ubah(id) {
      id.innerHTML = "Wait a minute, Processing......"
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
